About Execute
----------------------------------------------------------------------
This priject is not very perfect.
The Environment with Spyder and package if pygame are needed.
open the file "whale.py" and execute it, then you can start your test.
----------------------------------------------------------------------

About Edit
----------------------------------------------------------------------
If you want to change the species or even modify this game to another 
mini game about different knowledge:
open the file "whale_name.txt"
add the option in this order
example:
北露脊鯨 Eubalaena_Glacialis 1_1.jpg
that is

"Chinese name"(space)"scientific name"(space)"image"

Rule of naming images
"(Num)_1.jpg"
